rows.label: qst202909_msg0001
rows.name: Fumooh!!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0002
rows.name: Wh-What was that?!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0003
rows.name: I-I thought I was going to die, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0004
rows.name: Thank you for saving me, mo!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0005
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]So it wasn't Kastina.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0006
rows.name:
And who might you be?
What are you doing here?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0007
rows.name: Sage is Sage, mo!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm training day and night to
become a great Nopon Sage, mo!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0009
rows.name:
I was meditating here when I
got buried by the falling
snow and almost died, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0010
rows.name:
But I feel like I've reached some
kind of enlightenment, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0011
rows.name: What a shady Nopon...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0012
rows.name:
Still, he's a valuable source
of information. We need to
find out where Kastina went.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0013
rows.name:
Did you see a Luxurian girl? I
heard she was around here...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0014
rows.name: Fumomo...[ML:Dash ] A girl, mo?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0015
rows.name:
I might have seen one,
or I might not have...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0016
rows.name:
Make up your mind. A life
is on the line here.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0017
rows.name: Momo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0018
rows.name:
If you give me an offering, I
might remember something, mo.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0020
rows.name: How did it come to this?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0021
rows.name: I'm hungry and have no energy, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0022
rows.name:
If my stomach is full, I'm sure
I'll remember about that girl, mo!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0023
rows.name:
I don't really trust him, but
beggars can't be choosers.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0024
rows.name: Can't be helped. So what do you want?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0025
rows.name: Juicy Ray Fin and a Benign Cricket...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202909_msg0026
rows.name: And a Soft Sea Cucumber, please, mo!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0027
rows.name: Sage will be waiting here, mo!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0028
rows.name: Kastina!
